Overview

This report shows model results for:

  • Season: GRU_S1

Different rules are simulated on historical data to assess their effect on label quality.

Some figures:

  • Number of capture events: 41804
  • model accuracy overall: 89.79 %
  • model accuracy for high-confidence cases: 97.14 %
  • proportion of high-confidence cases: 77.96 %
